      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '10. Collision detection (2)


    Behind this slide, you will find an
    example of a high-speed Rigidbody simulation (press P to start it when you''re
    close). Try changing the collision detection methods of the various rigidbodies
    to see how the behaviour changes.


    The simulation objects can be found in
    the Hierarchy, inside SimulatorHighSpeed.'
