  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '2. Solid objects (1)


    Look at the ball on the right. You may find
    it in the Hierarchy as Objects > Sphere_NoCollider. This object currently only
    defines a Transform component and a mesh layer, defining its geometry.


    If
    you try, you will notice that your character can move cleanly through it, as
    there is nothing preventing it from doing that. The component devoted to this
    task is called a Collider.


    Select the ball GameObject and add a SphereCollider
    component to it.

'
