  m_text: '16. Trigger colliders (3)


    EXERCISE 5: Add a trigger collider that
    covers the inside of the goal. Add a script on the Goal object that, whenever
    the Football enters the goal, logs "Goal!" and the number of goals scored so
    far to the console. '
