  m_text: "15. Trigger colliders (2)\n\nvoid OnTriggerEnter(Collider col)\n// Called
    at the first frame that \"col\" enters the trigger collider on the controlled
    object. \n\nvoid OnTriggerExit(Collider col)\n// Called at the first frame that
    \"col\" is not intersecting the trigger collider anymore.\n\nvoid OnTriggerStay(Collider
    col)\n// Called for all frames, for all colliders that are intersecting the trigger
    collider on the controlled object\n"
